    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Concessio in <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">emphiteusim</rs> unius
                            <rs key="#Houses">mansionis</rs> cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions">solo
                            terrę</rs> positę <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/594">Ravennę</placeName> in
                        regione Sancti Stephani apud <rs key="#Walls">murum</rs> 
                        <rs key="#Cities">civitatis</rs>, facta a <persName><name ref="Fuscardus Petri">Fuscardo
                            Petri</name></persName> et ab eius filiorum favore 
                        <persName key="#Medical_doctors"><name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName> 
                        <rs key="#Medical_doctors">medici</rs> et <persName><name ref="Berta">Berthę
                        </name></persName> eius uxoris,
                        filiorum et unius successoris mediocris personę; calciarium solidorum 20
                        Lucensium. Actum Ravennę, rog. <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannis
                        </name></persName> <rs key="#Notary">notarii</rs>, 1131, 20 augusti, ind.
                        IX.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p>Mezzetti, <foreign>Le carte</foreign>, vol. 2, doc. 171 (in preparazione).</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
